&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community Engagement Specialist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://study.com/&quot;&gt;Study.com&lt;/a&gt; is the leading educational website with lessons, courses and practice for students, teachers, and adult learners. We are seeking a skilled and dynamic Community Engagement Specialist to join our team as a contractor and to monitor relevant subreddits for discussions and participate in Reddit discussions by providing genuinely helpful, informative responses that naturally highlight Study.com&#39;s value. This is a fully remote, online contract role. All work is paid hourly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Monitor relevant subreddits for discussions related to our brand and our products.&lt;br&gt;- Participate in Reddit discussions by providing genuinely helpful, informative responses that naturally highlight Study.com&#39;s value where relevant&lt;br&gt;- Build a credible, trusted presence across relevant subreddits through consistent, long-term engagement&lt;br&gt;- Identify trending topics, pain points, and questions within the online education space to inform engagement opportunities&lt;br&gt;- Track Study.com brand mentions across Reddit and respond to inquiries, reviews, and comments in a timely and authentic manner&lt;br&gt;- Flag negative sentiment, misinformation, or competitor mentions to the team for escalation&lt;br&gt;- Submit daily activity logs with links to all posts, comments, and interactions completed during each shift&lt;br&gt;- Provide weekly performance summaries highlighting wins, challenges, and recommendations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- At least 2 years of proven experience engaging on Reddit (i.e., a Reddit account that is at least 2 years old with an established history) OR at least 2 years of community engagement experience on other platforms.&lt;br&gt;- Deep familiarity with Reddit&#39;s ecosystem: subreddit cultures, community norms, posting etiquette, and what gets flagged or removed&lt;br&gt;- Strong writing skills with a natural, conversational tone; ability to craft responses that are helpful and informative first, promotional second&lt;br&gt;- Understanding of how community platform engagement contributes to brand visibility and Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)&lt;br&gt;- Self-motivated and capable of maintaining consistent engagement over the long term without direct supervision&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reliable Payments: &lt;/strong&gt;You&#39;ll receive payments twice a month and automated invoicing for your work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote Work: &lt;/strong&gt;This is a fully online contracted work-from-home opportunity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexibility: &lt;/strong&gt;Work when you want, where you want, and select projects that most interest you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support: &lt;/strong&gt;Our supportive staff is available answer your questions and help you get up and running.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Contract Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete the application and submit with your resume.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applications are approved and contracts sent on Wednesdays.&lt;/li&gt;
