&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SEO/AEO Content Writer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://Study.com&quot;&gt;Study.com&lt;/a&gt; is the leading educational website with lessons, courses and practice for students, teachers, and adult learners. We are seeking a skilled and dynamic Content Writer to join our team as a contractor and support us in creating high-quality education content for our primarily US-based users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fully remote, online contract role. All work is paid hourly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This role involves researching, outlining, writing, editing, and optimizing content related to education and test preparation. You will create original, high-performance content designed not only to rank in traditional search results, but also to be cited and surfaced in AI-powered search environments (e.g., Google AI Overviews and generative engines). Success in this role requires balancing SEO best practices with emerging Engine Optimization (EO) principles to improve visibility, citation share, and AI-driven discoverability.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Tasks may include:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Researching about education and test prep topics for a U.S.-based audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing detailed outlines based on keyword research, competitor analysis, and content briefs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing SEO/EO-optimized articles that balance search performance with readability and user intent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorporating marketing claims and product messaging seamlessly into informative content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyzing performance data and generating insights to guide content improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Editing and optimizing existing published articles for improved rankings, visibility and engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating infographics or visual elements to increase shareability and link potential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring all content is unique, accurate, well-structured, and aligned with brand voice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Availability to work with overlap in Pacific Standard Time (minimum of 4 hours between 1 PM – 8 PM PST)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 - 5+ years of professional experience writing SEO/EO optimized driven content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in marketing content, link-building content, or performance-driven publishing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leveraging AI writing and research tools (e.g., ChatGPT, Claude, Surfer, Clearscope) to enhance content quality, efficiency, SEO performance, and ideation, while maintaining strong editorial judgment and human oversight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong copyediting skills with exceptional attention to grammar, clarity, and consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success publishing content that drives organic traffic, backlinks, and engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of on-page SEO best practices, including:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keyword research and search intent alignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitor analysis and SERP evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic header structure (H1–H3 hierarchy)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Metadata optimization (title tags, meta descriptions)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Internal linking strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Readability optimization and user experience considerations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to incorporate keywords naturally without sacrificing quality or authority&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience optimizing content for both user experience and search engine performance&lt;/li&gt;
