&lt;p&gt;Study.com is a leader in online education, helping millions of learners reach their academic and career goals. We&#39;re expanding our short-form and long-form video presence across **YouTube and TikTok.** We produce high-quality videos that teach test strategies, explain key concepts, walk learners through practice problems, and help adult learners make smarter education decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for **confident, engaging on-camera presenters** who can work across both long-form (YouTube) and short-form (TikTok) formats — and make complex topics feel simple and approachable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a remote, contract role. All work is paid per video.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will record videos using scripts and practice problems we provide, across two formats:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YouTube long-form&lt;/strong&gt; (typically under 10 minutes): test strategies, exam overviews, content explanations, and step-by-step practice problem walkthroughs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TikTok short-form&lt;/strong&gt; (~1 minute): fast-paced tips, hooks, quick problem demos, and career or degree-completion advice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Examples of video topics:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 Easy Strategies to Stay Motivated for the Praxis Exam&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practice Problems for ASVAB Mathematics Knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TOEFL® Speaking Task 1: How to Answer in 45 Seconds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How to Earn Your Bachelor&#39;s Degree in 2 Years with Degree Hacked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your goal: make test prep and degree-completion content feel &lt;strong&gt;confident, approachable, and effective&lt;/strong&gt; for adult learners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No editing is required.&lt;/strong&gt; We&#39;re looking for creators who are confident presenting clearly on camera.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record engaging, instructional videos for &lt;strong&gt;YouTube (long-form)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;TikTok (short-form)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver content in a clear, concise, and encouraging style.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a consistent, professional on-screen presence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate educational concepts using a &lt;strong&gt;dry-erase board, tablet/stylus, or pen-and-paper&lt;/strong&gt; with clear and readable handwriting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow &lt;a href=&quot;http://Study.com&quot;&gt;Study.com&lt;/a&gt;&#39;s brand and presenter guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorporate feedback and revise delivery as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
