&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video experience:&lt;/strong&gt; Proven experience creating content for YouTube, TikTok, or similar platforms — including both short-form (vertical 9:16) and long-form (16:9) work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On-camera skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Confident, natural presenter who can explain complex ideas simply and connect with the viewer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equipment:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
