&lt;li&gt;External microphone for clear audio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good lighting for recording&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tablet/stylus or dry-erase board&lt;/strong&gt; (and printer if needed) for demonstrations and practice problem walkthroughs&lt;/li&gt;
